#: ../../../en/history.rst:90
msgid ""
"Arguments like ``-x`` / ``--exitfirst``, ``-l`` / ``--showlocals``, "
"``--fulltrace``, ``--pdb``, ``-S`` / ``--nocapture`` (``-s`` / "
"``--capture=off`` today), ``--collectonly`` (``--collect-only`` today)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../en/history.rst:95
msgid ""
"In the same month, the ``py`` library `gets split off "
