" from ``PyPy``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../en/history.rst:99
msgid ""
"It seemed to get rather quiet for a while, and little seemed to happen "
"between October 2004 (removing ``py`` from PyPy) and January 2007 (first "
"commit in the now-pytest repository). However, there were various "
"discussions about features/ideas on the mailinglist, and :pypi:`a couple "
"of releases <py/0.8.0-alpha2/#history>` every couple of months:"
msgstr ""

